=== 2.0 Lists ===

{{info}}Some of the mentioned styles do not work on all browsers. For a comprehensive list follow [[this link>>http://www.quirksmode.org/css/lists.html]].{{/info}}

|=Feature|=XWiki Syntax {{velocity}}$crtSyntaxVer{{/velocity}}|=Result
|Bulleted list|((({{{
* item 1
** item 2
*** item 3
* item 4
}}})))|(((
* item 1
** item 2
*** item 3
* item 4
)))
|Numbered list|((({{{
1. item 1
11. item 2
111. item 3
1. item 4
}}})))|(((
